Event.create(startYear: 1993, startMonth: 3, startDay: 21, startTime: '', endYear: '', endMonth: '', endDay: '', endTime: '', displayDate: '', headline: 'Publication of translation of Kitáb-i-Aqdas into English', text: 'The Kitáb-i-Aqdas—the Book described in such exalted terms by the Guardian of the Cause of God as “that priceless treasury enshrining for all time the brightest emanations of the mind of Bahá’u’lláh, the Charter of His World Order, the chief repository of His laws, the Harbinger of His Covenant, the Pivotal Work containing some of His noblest exhortations, weightiest pronouncements, and portentous prophecies, and revealed during the full tide of His tribulations, at a time when the rulers of the earth had definitely forsaken Him”—this Most Holy Book, we have the honor to announce, will, in a copiously annotated English translation, be released to the Community of Bahá at Naw-Rúz.', media: '', mediaCredit: '', mediaCaption: '', mediaThumbnail: '', eventtype_id: 2, eventgroup_id: 10, background: '')
